---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="POS Glowverse - Mas Muhammad" description="A point-of-sale and seller commerce platform for MS Glow cosmetics brand enabling product and inventory management, complete shopping cart order lifecycle with multi-status workflow, payment processing via Xendit, shipment tracking with AWB integration, invoice management, chat messaging, and real-time dashboard analytics. Built with C# (.NET 6) and Go microservices with clean architecture.">
  <nav>
    <a href="/portfolio" class="nav-logo">MAS<span>.</span>MUH</a>
    <a href="/portfolio" class="nav-back">&larr; Back to Portfolio</a>
    <button class="theme-toggle" id="themeToggle" aria-label="Toggle theme">
      <span class="theme-icon-light">&#9728;&#65039;</span>
      <span class="theme-icon-dark">&#127769;</span>
    </button>
    <button class="nav-hamburger" id="navHamburger" aria-label="Open menu">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
  </nav>

  <!-- MOBILE NAV PANEL -->
  <div class="mobile-overlay" id="mobileOverlay"></div>
  <div class="mobile-nav" id="mobileNav">
    <div class="mobile-nav-header">
      <div class="nav-logo">MAS<span>.</span>MUH</div>
      <button class="mobile-nav-close" id="mobileNavClose" aria-label="Close menu">&#10005;</button>
    </div>
    <ul class="mobile-nav-links">
      <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#skills">Skills</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#experience">Experience</a></li>
      <li><a href="/portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
    <button class="mobile-nav-toggle" id="mobileThemeToggle">Toggle Theme</button>
  </div>

  <div class="pos-glowverse">

<header class="pos-glowverse-hero">
    <div class="pos-glowverse-hero-meta">
      <span class="pos-glowverse-badge badge-consulting">Consulting</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-badge pos-glowverse-badge-domain">E-commerce / POS</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-badge pos-glowverse-badge-year">February 2024</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="pos-glowverse-hero-title">
      POS<br>
      <span>Glowverse</span><span class="pos-glowverse-cursor"></span>
    </h1>
    <p class="pos-glowverse-hero-desc">
      A point-of-sale and seller commerce platform for MS Glow cosmetics brand enabling
      product and inventory management, complete shopping cart order lifecycle with
      multi-status workflow, payment processing via Xendit, shipment tracking with AWB
      integration, invoice management, chat messaging, and real-time dashboard analytics.
      Built with C# (.NET 6) and Go microservices with clean architecture.
    </p>
    <div class="pos-glowverse-stack-pills">
      <span class="pos-glowverse-stack-pill">C# .NET 6</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-stack-pill">Go 1.17</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-stack-pill">MongoDB</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-stack-pill">Xendit</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-stack-pill">Twilio</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-stack-pill">JWT Auth</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-stack-pill">Docker + K8s</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="pos-glowverse-section">
    <div class="pos-glowverse-section-label">
      <span class="pos-glowverse-section-label-num">01</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-section-label-text">Impact &amp; Metrics</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-section-label-line"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="pos-glowverse-metrics-grid">
      <div class="pos-glowverse-metric-card"><div class="pos-glowverse-metric-val">60K+</div><div class="pos-glowverse-metric-label">Lines of Code</div><div class="pos-glowverse-metric-sub">C# + Go + Razor</div></div>
      <div class="pos-glowverse-metric-card"><div class="pos-glowverse-metric-val">108+</div><div class="pos-glowverse-metric-label">API Endpoints</div><div class="pos-glowverse-metric-sub">RESTful + Go services</div></div>
      <div class="pos-glowverse-metric-card"><div class="pos-glowverse-metric-val">50+</div><div class="pos-glowverse-metric-label">Database Models</div><div class="pos-glowverse-metric-sub">MongoDB collections</div></div>
      <div class="pos-glowverse-metric-card pos-glowverse-red"><div class="pos-glowverse-metric-val">10</div><div class="pos-glowverse-metric-label">Complexity Score</div><div class="pos-glowverse-metric-sub">Mission Critical</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="pos-glowverse-business-line-cards">
      <div class="pos-glowverse-bl-card"><div class="pos-glowverse-bl-card-title">Order Management</div><div class="pos-glowverse-bl-card-desc">Complete order lifecycle with checkout, approval, picking, shipment, delivery, receive, close, cancel, force-close, and manual received workflows.</div><span class="pos-glowverse-bl-card-tag">Order Lifecycle</span></div>
      <div class="pos-glowverse-bl-card"><div class="pos-glowverse-bl-card-title">Payments &amp; Finance</div><div class="pos-glowverse-bl-card-desc">Xendit payment gateway integration for transactions, balance management, withdrawal history, invoice processing, account receivable, and callbacks.</div><span class="pos-glowverse-bl-card-tag pos-glowverse-amber-tag">Xendit Gateway</span></div>
      <div class="pos-glowverse-bl-card"><div class="pos-glowverse-bl-card-title">Seller Commerce</div><div class="pos-glowverse-bl-card-desc">Seller registration, product management with margin/markup rules, inventory sync, outlet management, discount/promo engine, and dashboard analytics.</div><span class="pos-glowverse-bl-card-tag">Seller Tools</span></div>
      <div class="pos-glowverse-bl-card"><div class="pos-glowverse-bl-card-title">Communications</div><div class="pos-glowverse-bl-card-desc">In-app chat, WhatsApp/SMS via Twilio, email via MailKit, push notifications, and background workers for settlement, AWB updates, and approval expiry.</div><span class="pos-glowverse-bl-card-tag pos-glowverse-amber-tag">Twilio + MailKit</span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pos-glowverse-section">
    <div class="pos-glowverse-section-label">
      <span class="pos-glowverse-section-label-num">02</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-section-label-text">Architecture</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-section-label-line"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="pos-glowverse-arch-diagram">
      <div class="pos-glowverse-arch-diagram-inner">
        <div class="pos-glowverse-arch-node pos-glowverse-source"><div class="pos-glowverse-arch-node-icon"></div><div class="pos-glowverse-arch-node-label">API Client</div><div class="pos-glowverse-arch-node-sub">Mobile / Web</div></div>
        <div class="pos-glowverse-arch-arrow"><div class="pos-glowverse-arch-arrow-line"></div><div class="pos-glowverse-arch-arrow-label">HTTPS</div></div>
        <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:0;">
          <div class="pos-glowverse-arch-node core" style="width:220px;">
            <div class="pos-glowverse-arch-node-label" style="font-size:13px; margin-bottom:10px;">Backend Services</div>
            <div class="pos-glowverse-core-stack">
              <div class="pos-glowverse-core-step"><div class="pos-glowverse-core-step-dot"></div>C# Web API (26+ Controllers)</div>
              <div class="pos-glowverse-core-step"><div class="pos-glowverse-core-step-dot"></div>Go App Service (Auth)</div>
              <div class="pos-glowverse-core-step"><div class="pos-glowverse-core-step-dot"></div>Application Layer (40+ Services)</div>
              <div class="pos-glowverse-core-step"><div class="pos-glowverse-core-step-dot" style="background:var(--blue)"></div>Scheduler Workers (4)</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pos-glowverse-arch-arrow"><div class="pos-glowverse-arch-arrow-line"></div><div class="pos-glowverse-arch-arrow-label">persist</div></div>
        <div class="pos-glowverse-arch-node pos-glowverse-output"><div class="pos-glowverse-arch-node-icon"></div><div class="pos-glowverse-arch-node-label">MongoDB</div><div class="pos-glowverse-arch-node-sub">Primary database</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pos-glowverse-section">
    <div class="pos-glowverse-section-label">
      <span class="pos-glowverse-section-label-num">03</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-section-label-text">Tech Stack</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-section-label-line"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="pos-glowverse-impact-wrapper">
      <table class="pos-glowverse-stack-table">
        <tbody>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Runtime (C#)</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">.NET 6.0</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Runtime (Go)</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">Go 1.17</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Web Framework (C#)</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">ASP.NET Core + AutoMapper + Swagger</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Web Framework (Go)</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">Go-Chi with JWT middleware</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Database</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">MongoDB (primary) + PostgreSQL + MySQL</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Payment Gateway</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">Xendit (invoice, VA, transfer, disbursement)</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Messaging</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">Twilio (WhatsApp/SMS) + MailKit (Email)</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Auth</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">JWT Bearer + Basic Auth + Bcrypt</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Background Jobs</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">NCrontab Workers (Settlement, AWB, Approval, Sync)</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Monitoring</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">Elastic APM + Logrus</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Infrastructure</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">Docker + Kubernetes (GKE) + GitLab CI</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pos-glowverse-section">
    <div class="pos-glowverse-section-label">
      <span class="pos-glowverse-section-label-num">04</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-section-label-text">Capabilities</span>
      <span class="pos-glowverse-section-label-line"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="pos-glowverse-impact-wrapper">
      <table class="pos-glowverse-stack-table">
        <tbody>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Order Workflow</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">Checkout, approve, process, ready-to-pick, ship, receive, close, cancel, force-close, manual-receive</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Product Management</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">Catalog, inventory, pricing, margin/markup, stock sync, barcode scan, discount promo engine</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Payment Processing</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">Transaction, balance, withdrawal, invoice, callback, OTP confirmation, account receivable</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Shipment</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">Shipping rate, area management, tracking, AWB, pickup scheduling, callback tracking</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Dashboard</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">Best-selling products, low-stock alerts, transaction lists, seller performance metrics</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="pos-glowverse-layer">Auth &amp; Security</td><td class="pos-glowverse-tech">JWT tokens, Basic Auth, bcrypt passwords, session management, role-based access, rate limiting</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  </div>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-txt">&copy; 2026 Mas Muhammad</div>
    <div class="footer-txt">Built with <span>Astro</span></div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style is:global>

  .pos-glowverse {
    --pos-glowverse-bg: #0a0b0d;
    --pos-glowverse-bg2: #0f1114;
    --pos-glowverse-bg3: #141720;
    --pos-glowverse-surface: #1a1e28;
    --pos-glowverse-surface2: #212636;
    --pos-glowverse-border: #2a2f40;
    --pos-glowverse-border2: #363c50;
    --pos-glowverse-accent: #00e5a0;
    --pos-glowverse-accent2: #00b87a;
    --pos-glowverse-accent-dim: rgba(0, 229, 160, 0.08);
    --pos-glowverse-accent-dim2: rgba(0, 229, 160, 0.15);
    --pos-glowverse-amber: #f59e0b;
    --pos-glowverse-amber-dim: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
    --pos-glowverse-blue: #60a5fa;
    --pos-glowverse-blue-dim: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.1);
    --pos-glowverse-red: #f87171;
    --pos-glowverse-text: #e8eaf0;
    --pos-glowverse-text2: #8b92a8;
    --pos-glowverse-text3: #5a6077;
    --pos-glowverse-mono: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    --pos-glowverse-display: "Syne", sans-serif;
    --pos-glowverse-radius: 10px;
    --pos-glowverse-radius-lg: 16px;

    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 110px 32px 96px;
  }

  .pos-glowverse * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .pos-glowverse body {
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-bg);
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-text);
    font-family: var(--pos-glowverse-mono);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .pos-glowverse-nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--pos-glowverse-border);
  }
  .pos-glowverse-nav-back {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-text2);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-nav-back:hover {
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-accent);
  }
  .pos-glowverse-nav-back svg {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-nav-dot {
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-border2);
  }
  .pos-glowverse-nav-title {
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-text3);
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .pos-glowverse-hero {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .pos-glowverse-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-badge-corporate {
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-blue-dim);
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-blue);
    border-color: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.2);
  }
  .pos-glowverse-badge-client {
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-accent-dim);
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-accent);
    border-color: rgba(0, 229, 160, 0.2);
  }
  .pos-glowverse-badge-year {
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-surface);
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-text3);
    border-color: var(--pos-glowverse-border);
  }

  .pos-glowverse-hero-title {
    font-family: var(--pos-glowverse-display);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-hero-title span {
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-accent);
    position: relative;
  }

  .pos-glowverse-hero-desc {
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-text2);
    font-size: 14px;
    max-width: 620px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .pos-glowverse-stack-pills {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-stack-pill {
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--pos-glowverse-border);
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-text2);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-stack-pill:hover {
    border-color: var(--pos-glowverse-accent);
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-accent);
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-accent-dim);
  }

  .pos-glowverse-section {
    margin-bottom: 52px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-section-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-section-label-text {
    font-family: var(--pos-glowverse-display);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-text3);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-section-label-line {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-border);
  }
  .pos-glowverse-section-label-num {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-border2);
  }

  .pos-glowverse-metrics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-metric-card {
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-bg3);
    border: 1px solid var(--pos-glowverse-border);
    border-radius: var(--pos-glowverse-radius);
    padding: 20px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-metric-card::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-accent);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-metric-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--pos-glowverse-border2);
  }
  .pos-glowverse-metric-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-metric-amber .pos-glowverse-metric-val {
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-amber);
  }
  .pos-glowverse-metric-amber::before {
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-amber);
  }

  .pos-glowverse-metric-val {
    font-family: var(--pos-glowverse-display);
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-accent);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-metric-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-text2);
    margin-bottom: 3px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-metric-sub {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-text3);
  }

  .pos-glowverse-arch-diagram {
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-bg3);
    border: 1px solid var(--pos-glowverse-border);
    border-radius: var(--pos-glowverse-radius-lg);
    padding: 32px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-arch-diagram-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    row-gap: 24px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-arch-node {
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--pos-glowverse-border2);
    border-radius: var(--pos-glowverse-radius);
    padding: 14px 18px;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 130px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-core {
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-surface2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 229, 160, 0.3);
    min-width: 200px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-output {
    border-color: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.3);
  }
  .pos-glowverse-schema-node {
    border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-amber-dim);
    min-width: 110px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-arch-node-icon {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-arch-node-label {
    font-family: var(--pos-glowverse-display);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 3px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-arch-node-sub {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-text3);
    font-family: var(--pos-glowverse-mono);
  }

  .pos-glowverse-arch-arrow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 8px;
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-text3);
    font-size: 11px;
    gap: 4px;
    min-width: 60px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-arch-arrow-line {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      var(--pos-glowverse-border),
      var(--pos-glowverse-accent),
      var(--pos-glowverse-border)
    );
    position: relative;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-arch-arrow-line::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    right: -6px;
    top: -6px;
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-accent);
    font-size: 10px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-arch-arrow-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-text3);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .pos-glowverse-core-wrap {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-core-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-core-step {
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-bg3);
    border: 1px solid var(--pos-glowverse-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 7px 12px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--pos-glowverse-text2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .pos-glowverse-core-step-dot {
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--pos-glowverse-accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .pos-glowverse-schema-connector {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
  }
